1) To make a directory in hdfs
oza@ubuntu:/usr/local/bin/hadoop-2.7.3/bin$ ./hadoop fs -mkdir /h1b-data

2) To copy file from local to hdfs
oza@ubuntu:/usr/local/bin/hadoop-2.7.3/bin$ ./hadoop fs -copyFromLocal /usr/local/bin/dataset/h1b-data.csv /h1b-data

3) To delete a folder from hdfs
oza@ubuntu:/usr/local/bin/hadoop-2.7.3/bin$ ./hadoop fs -rm -r /h1b-data

4)To delete a file from hdfs
oza@ubuntu:/usr/local/bin/hadoop-2.7.3/bin$ ./hadoop fs -rm -r /h1b-ouput/most_petitions_denied_places_analysis.csv

